Video on Trial (season 9)
The ninth season of the Canadian television comedy series Video on Trial premiered on MuchMusic on June 8th, 2014. For this season, the series was revamped. Aisha Alfa and Paul Lemieux star in the new version. Season 9 uses a new format featuring reoccurring sketches and segments.
